title: Kissing Your Sister: The Story of a Tie
description: Behind the scenes of the Meyer administration during the historic House of Representatives vote.
quote: Daddy leaned into me and he said, ‘You know, a lot of people don’t like Nixon, but by God they respect him. And that’s you, peanut.’
